('No chemo', 'June 23, 2018', 'Patient has concerns regarding treatment with no chemo. Will not havnig chemo allow cancer to spread?', 'No chemo, 10 year tamoxife', 'Grade 1, 1/1 nodes, ER+/PR+, HER2- (IHC)', 'Lowrisk', 'Chemo', 'Oncologist recomended chemo; 4AC and 12 TAXOL. No chemotreatment, but onto 14th radiation treatment and prescribed tamoxifen for 10 years. Other pratient explains Tamoxifen prevents cancer from spreading, no need for chemo as of now.', 'Harrison Klinski', 'https://community.breastcancer.org/forum/145/topics/865395', '', ''),
