('One year appointment today with breast surgeon', 'Sept 2015', 'Curious whether scans are done for patients who had BMX', 'Left mastectomy, right prophylactic mastectomy, hormonal therapy, prophylactic ovary removal', 'ILC, Stage IIA, Grade 2, 0/4 nodes, ER+/PR+, HER2-', '', '', 'Scans are not usually done unless there is clear evidance that there is a problems. Your doctors can instead monitor your progress by frequent breast exams and blood work.', 'Amira Elfergani ', 'https://community.breastcancer.org/forum/145/topics/835056', '', ''),
