('Pregnant with Breast Cancer', 'august 2016 ', 'patient is interested in meeting others in a similar situation (pregnant while fighting BC)', 'had chemotherapy, a single right mastectomy, and lymph node removal  ', 'IDC, Right, 2cm, Grade 3, 2/30 nodes, ER+/PR+, HER2+ (FISH', '', '', 'In general, treatments like chemotherapy appears to be safe for the mother and child. Thus, pregnant patients can choose to start during or after pregnancy.', 'Amira Elfergani ', 'https://community.breastcancer.org/forum/145/topics/847250', '', ''),
