('Why are they afraid of me?', 'July 2014', 'The patient wants to know why her family and friends seem afraid of her and don\'t stay in touch with her', 'Radiation therapy (Breast and Lymph nodes), Hormonal Therapy (Aromasin), Lumpectomy RB, node dissection, and biopsy LB', ' IDC, 3cm, Stage IIA, Grade 1, 0/1 nodes, ER+/PR+, HER2-', 'Encouragement', '', 'People react differently when confronted with a difficult situation. Some handle it better than others and the ones that handle it badly can disappoint and leave the patient feeling like they are to blame. It is important to not blame yourself and cherish relationships with people who are actually there for you.', 'Preetham Ramesh', 'https://community.breastcancer.org/forum/145/topics/823006', '', ''),
